{"tid":2259590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"世貿正式授權歐盟對40億美元美國商品徵收關稅","createTime":"2020-10-27T03:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T03:06:52.000Z","uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3ef959c6fe90c839cad3dca6da8491c35527cd89","tid":2259590,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:01:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556748-20201026.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556748-20201026.htm&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETYMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=01a25fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556748-20201026.htm&h=9b5c5153\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556748-20201026.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界貿易組織正式授權歐盟對40億美元的美國商品徵收關稅，以報復美國非法補貼飛機製造商波音。<br />\n<br />\n世貿的決定，標誌歐盟在世貿掃清對美國商品採取合法報復的最後一道障礙，但預料歐盟不會在美國下月大選前採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n美國駐世貿官員敦促歐盟不要對美國商品徵稅，駐世貿代表團亦發表聲明，指特朗普政府強烈主張透過協商，解決長達16年的爭端，並尋求達成合理和解，創造公平競爭環境，如果歐盟採取關稅行動，將迫使美國回應，雙方將會進一步偏離解決爭端的軌道。"},{"pid":"583c14566c84be754594e62a692caf6115975eba","tid":2259590,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左膠又贏"},{"pid":"ad5c394850db73c97a560920cc3e631d3b1a4b1f","tid":2259590,"uid":274435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T03:06:52.000Z","msg":"咁iPhone 係咪會貴左？"}]}